871
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:48,360
Isn't this making too big a deal of it?

872
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:49,800
Not at all.

873
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:52,000
This is our grand joint launch event.

874
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,680
The sense of occasion must be maxed out.

875
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:55,320
Alright then.

876
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,040
Good luck.

877
00:42:56,520 --> 00:42:57,040
Good luck.
